Name: Passerby of Wandering Cloud
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Outgoing Healing by 10%. | Four Set Effect: At the start of the battle, immediately regenerates 1 Skill Point.

Name: Musketeer of Wild Wheat
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: ATK increases by 12%. | Four Set Effect: The wearer's SPD increases by 6% and Basic ATK DMG increases by 10%.

Name: Knight of Purity Palace
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases DEF by 15%. | Four Set Effect: Increases the max DMG that can be absorbed by the Shield created by the wearer by 20%.

Name: Hunter of Glacial Forest
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Ice DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: After the wearer uses their Ultimate, their CRIT DMG increases by 25% for 2 turn(s).

Name: Champion of Streetwise Boxing
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Physical DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: After the wearer attacks or is hit, their ATK increases by 5% for the rest of the battle. This effect can stack up to 5 time(s).

Name: Guard of Wuthering Snow
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Reduces DMG taken by 8%. | Four Set Effect: At the beginning of the turn, if the wearer's HP is equal to or less than 50%, restores HP equal to 8% of their Max HP and regenerates 5 Energy.

Name: Firesmith of Lava-Forging
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Fire DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: Increases the wearer's Skill DMG by 12%. After unleashing Ultimate, increases the wearer's Fire DMG by 12% for the next attack.

Name: Genius of Brilliant Stars
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Quantum DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: When the wearer deals DMG to the target enemy, ignores 10% DEF. If the target enemy has Quantum Weakness, the wearer additionally ignores 10% DEF.

Name: Band of Sizzling Thunder
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Lightning DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: When the wearer uses their Skill, increases the wearer's ATK by 20% for 1 turn(s).

Name: Eagle of Twilight Line
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Wind DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: After the wearer uses their Ultimate, their action is Advanced Forward by 25%.

Name: Thief of Shooting Meteor
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Break Effect by 16%. | Four Set Effect: Increases the wearer's Break Effect by 16%. When the wearer inflicts Weakness Break on an enemy, regenerates 3 Energy.

Name: Wastelander of Banditry Desert
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases Imaginary DMG by 10%. | Four Set Effect: When attacking debuffed enemies, the wearer's CRIT Rate increases by 10%, and their CRIT DMG increases by 20% against Imprisoned enemies.

Name: Space Sealing Station
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's ATK increases by an extra 12%.

Name: Fleet of the Ageless
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's Max HP by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, all allies' ATK increases by 8%.

Name: Pan-Galactic Commercial Enterprise
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's Effect Hit Rate by 10%. Meanwhile, the wearer's ATK increases by an amount that is equal to 25% of the current Effect Hit Rate, up to a maximum of 25%.

Name: Belobog of the Architects
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's DEF by 15%. When the wearer's Effect Hit Rate is 50% or higher, the wearer gains an extra 15% DEF.

Name: Celestial Differentiator
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's CRIT DMG by 16%. When the wearer's current CRIT DMG reaches 120% or higher, after entering battle, the wearer's CRIT Rate increases by 60% until the end of their first attack.

Name: Inert Salsotto
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 8%. When the wearer's current CRIT Rate reaches 50% or higher, the wearer's Ultimate and follow-up attack DMG increases by 15%.

Name: Talia: Kingdom of Banditry
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's Break Effect by 16%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 145 or higher, the wearer's Break effect increases by an extra 20%.

Name: Sprightly Vonwacq
SetEffect: Two Set Effect: Increases the wearer's Energy Regeneration Rate by 5%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's action is Advanced Forward by 40% immediately upon entering battle.
